---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="V8V88V8V88 | Vaibhav Pratap Singh"
  description="Developer, Linux enthusiast, and open source contributor. Building things with Rust, C++, TypeScript & more."
  canonical="https://v8v88v8v88.com/"
  twitterSite="@v8v88v8v88"
  twitterCreator="@v8v88v8v88"
  showRss={true}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "url": "https://v8v88v8v88.com/",
      "name": "V8V88V8V88"
    })} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Person",
      "url": "https://v8v88v8v88.com/",
      "name": "Vaibhav Pratap Singh",
      "alternateName": "V8V88V8V88",
      "jobTitle": "Developer & Open Source Contributor",
      "image": "https://v8v88v8v88.com/images/image.webp",
      "sameAs": [
        "https://github.com/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://t.me/V8V88V8V88",
        "https://www.youtube.com/c/MagicalV8",
        "https://www.instagram.com/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://twitter.com/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://www.reddit.com/user/v8v88v8v88",
        "https://www.linkedin.com/in/v8v88v8v88/",
        "https://fosstodon.org/@v8v88v8v88"
      ],
      "knowsAbout": ["Linux", "FOSS", "Computer Science", "Software Development", "Web Design"]
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>$ &gt;[V8V88V8V88]_</h1>
    </section>

    <section class="intro">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <div class="avatar-flip" id="avatar-flip" onclick="this.classList.toggle('flipped')">
          <div class="avatar-inner">
            <img src="/images/image.webp" alt="Vaibhav" class="avatar-front" />
            <img src="/images/V8.webp" alt="V8" class="avatar-back" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-text">
          <h2>
            Hi, I'm
            <span class="vaibhav-hover" data-text="V8V88V8V88"
              onmouseenter="document.getElementById('avatar-flip').classList.add('flipped')"
              onmouseleave="document.getElementById('avatar-flip').classList.remove('flipped')">Vaibhav</span>
          </h2>
          <p>Linux × FOSS × Code × Design</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>
        Hi there! I'm
        <span>Vaibhav Pratap Singh</span>, known online as
        <span>V8</span>. A computer science student with a minor in AI & ML, and a strong interest in computers, the internet, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linux" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Linux</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Free_and_open-source_software" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">FOSS</a>, design, and coding. Naturally drawn toward understanding how systems work under the hood, with a growing focus on <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Low-level_programming_language" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">low-level programming</a> and <a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Rust</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Most learning and building are shaped by
        <a href="https://principles-wiki.net/principles:keep_it_simple_stupid" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">KISS</a>
        and the
        <a href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Unix_philosophy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Unix philosophy</a>, driven by curiosity and hands-on experimentation. Along the way, experience has also grown across full-stack development (mainly for practical and earning needs), as well as graphic design and video editing, which came naturally while working across different areas of computers. Interests often extend beyond code into reading, philosophy, history, geography, and scientific literature, usually wherever curiosity leads.
      </p>
      <p>
        Feel free to reach out via <a href="/contact/">social handles</a>, replies might take some time.
      </p>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iQFjSzPWcSA3sAt4WS-uKIUd7ReCz_hz/view?usp=sharing" class="resume-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resume</a>
    </section>

    <section class="projects">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <a href="/projects/" class="view-all">view all →</a>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li class="project-item">
          <a href="https://github.com/v8v88v8v88/indx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="/images/indx.webp" alt="INDX Project" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>INDX</h3>
            <p>Indexing everything that can be on maps</p>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="project-item">
          <a href="https://piracyindex.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="/images/piracyindex.webp" alt="piracy index website" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>The Piracy Index Website</h3>
            <p>The greatest Piracy Site which indexes all the greatest piracy sites around the web.</p>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="project-item">
          <a href="https://github.com/V8V88V8V88/telegram-gtk4-theme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="/images/telegram.webp" alt="telegram client with my theme" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Telegram - Libadwaita Theme</h3>
            <p>GTK4 / Libadwaita theme for Telegram Desktop of Linux/Windows/MacOS</p>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="project-item">
          <a href="https://github.com/V8V88V8V88/face-recognition" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="/images/facerecognition.webp" alt="face recognition program image" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>Face Recognition using CV2</h3>
            <p>The project I had to make for some funny reasons of my college.</p>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="project-item">
          <a href="https://github.com/V8V88V8V88/vfetch" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="/images/vfetch.webp" alt="terminal windows running vfetch" loading="lazy" />
            <h3>vfetch</h3>
            <p>The shortest best optimized alternative for vfetch made to run in all POSIX shells</p>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="posts">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Blogs</h2>
        <a href="/blogs/" class="view-all">view all →</a>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/minimalism/">
            <h3>Minimalism</h3>
            <p>How ultimate simplicity changed the design of my life.</p>
            <small><time>Oct 6, 2025</time></small>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/username/">
            <h3>Username</h3>
            <p>The only description of my username "V8" on internet you can find.</p>
            <small><time>Mar 4, 2025</time></small>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <a href="https://github.com/v8v88v8v88" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
          <span>GitHub</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://t.me/V8V88V8V88" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-telegram"></i>
          <span>Telegram</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/MagicalV8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
          <span>YouTube</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/v8v88v8v88" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
          <span>Instagram</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/v8v88v8v88" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
          <span>Twitter</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/v8v88v8v88" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-reddit"></i>
          <span>Reddit</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://myanimelist.net/profile/V8V88V8V88" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fas fa-film"></i>
          <span>MyAnimeList</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/v8v88v8v88/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
          <span>LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://fosstodon.org/@v8v88v8v88" target="_blank" rel="me noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fab fa-mastodon"></i>
          <span>Mastodon</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://v8v88v8v88.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
          <span>Website</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    var vaibhavHover = document.querySelector(".vaibhav-hover");
    var hoverText = vaibhavHover ? vaibhavHover.dataset.text : "";
    if (vaibhavHover) {
      vaibhavHover.textContent = "Vaibhav";
      vaibhavHover.addEventListener("mouseenter", function() { vaibhavHover.textContent = hoverText; });
      vaibhavHover.addEventListener("mouseleave", function() { vaibhavHover.textContent = "Vaibhav"; });
    }
    var projectsContainer = document.querySelector(".projects ul");
    if (projectsContainer) {
      var leftArrow = document.createElement("div");
      var rightArrow = document.createElement("div");
      leftArrow.classList.add("arrow", "left");
      rightArrow.classList.add("arrow", "right");
      leftArrow.innerHTML = '<i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>';
      rightArrow.innerHTML = '<i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>';
      document.querySelector(".projects").prepend(leftArrow);
      document.querySelector(".projects").append(rightArrow);
      leftArrow.addEventListener("click", function() { projectsContainer.scrollLeft -= projectsContainer.offsetWidth; });
      rightArrow.addEventListener("click", function() { projectsContainer.scrollLeft += projectsContainer.offsetWidth; });
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .hero h1::after {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 3px;
    height: 0.9em;
    background: #1DB954;
    margin-left: 2px;
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    vertical-align: baseline;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .section-header h2 { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .view-all {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45) !important;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    background: none !important;
    border: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }
  .view-all:hover { color: #1DB954 !important; }
  :global(body.light-mode) .view-all { color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45) !important; }
  :global(body.light-mode) .view-all:hover { color: #0f4d1f !important; }
  .intro .avatar-flip {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    perspective: 800px;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .intro .avatar-inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }
  .intro .avatar-flip.flipped .avatar-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .intro .avatar-flip img {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    border-radius: 50%;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
  .intro .avatar-back { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .intro .avatar-flip { width: 100px; height: 100px; } }
  @media (max-width: 480px) { .intro .avatar-flip { width: 80px; height: 80px; } }
</style>
